show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Vikram Rathod lies to his daughter that he has remarried and that her stepmother will soon come home. Meanwhile, Avni tries to convince everyone that she’s married too. At one point, Avni and Vikram cross paths. What happens next?
